PRIVACY POLICY

RiftsMUD collects only what is needed to run the game:

  - Character name, password hash, and save file data
  - Connection IP address and login times (standard MUD logging)
  - In-game mail, posts, and logged commands where applicable

We do not sell player data. Staff may review logs to investigate harassment,
bug reports, or rule violations.

Do not put real-world personal information (address, phone, financial data)
in character descriptions, mail, or public channels.

